{"tid":2403760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸軍民文宣戰 傳軍方訂新法禁網 中方否認技術人員抵仰光","createTime":"2021-02-11T09:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T09:54:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5081ec282ebb96a860c9193c2dfa3d33a0e4f2","tid":2403760,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"緬甸全國多處連續第六日示威爭取民主、反對軍事政變，目前不完全統計，全國約200多人被捕，部分人簽不再示威獲釋。在過去數日，軍方及示威者分別都打文宣戰，親軍方國營電視台播出中學生在戲棚內上課，然後宣稱首都內比都有學校繼續開課，不受全國罷工影響。但有分參與「上課」的一名學生揭發，有關片段「造馬」去年錄製，是「假新聞」。<br />\n<br />\n而數百名示威者在位於仰光的中國駐緬大使館外示威，高舉「停止幫助軍事政變」、「緬甸華人反對軍方政變」、「停止干涉我們的國家事務」等中文標語。在俄羅斯大使館外也有類似示威。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38091/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3-38104/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E8%BB%8D%E6%B0%91%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E6%88%B0-%E5%82%B3%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%82%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E7%B6%B2-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%B5%E4%BB%B0%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38091%2F%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%25AE%258A-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3-38104%2F%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A8%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E7%25B6%25B2-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258A%25B5%25E4%25BB%25B0%25E5%2585%2589&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=0a7fcd37\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38091/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3-38104/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E8%BB%8D%E6%B0%91%E6%96%87%E5%AE%A3%E6%88%B0-%E5%82%B3%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%82%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E7%B6%B2-%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%B5%E4%BB%B0